definition: to prepare/get ready/to provide or equip

sentences.english: Bedding is not provided, so bring a sleeping bag.

sentences.english: Participants should bring their own sticks, mouth guard, shin pads.

sentences.english: If you are self-provided please tell us.

sentences.english: I am only looking to gather the information below for Certified Used or Certified Pre-Owned vehicles.

sentences.english: Students should use their own padlocks to secure the lockers during the locker rental period.

sentences.english: Who serves as a soldier at his own expense?

sentences.english: If only I had a car of my own. I could drive it everywhere.
sentences.chinese: 要是有一辆自备车该多好啊，我可以开车到处兜风。
